txt.en: Khorroz can be found in Máttugard.\n\nYou should collect dwarf trinkets at Khorroz.
Place the dwarf trinkets in a supply chest
A supply chest can be found at any dwarf outpost in Máttugard.\n\nYou should place the dwarf trinkets in a supply chest.

Khorroz, once the home to the largest bat population in Gundabad, has now been overtaken by deadly cave-beasts. The dwarf-made cavern is littered with bones and old trinkets. These trinkets must have been collected by the cave-beasts as they hunt in Gundabad. Reuniting these trinkets with their rightful owners would certainly be a boon to the spirits of those seeking to reclaim Gundabad.
